          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Expert judgement (Urs Luginbühl, Swiss Sawmilling industry, personal communication in June 2014). Wood chips from softwood should have a price of 0.101 EUR/kg. Woodchips from hardwood should have a price of 0.112 EUR/kg. Average of these two values is used. Cross-reference; FAOSTAT database; http://faostat.fao.org/site/626/DesktopDefault.aspx?PageID=626#ancor; Average import/export prices of EU for 'chips and particles'. Price: 48.76 Euro/m3. The density of the wood chips is 650 kg/m3. The price is recalculated accordingly.</comment>
